{"tid":1615208,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"洪水橋建環保運輸系統 捷運巴士電車三選一","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T04:29:01.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0a1286d892379da0a8a51ee1d6ac61fe3a9bd2","tid":1615208,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hskefts.hk/img/tc/eval.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hskefts.hk%2Fimg%2Ftc%2Feval.png&h=e84ffba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hskefts.hk/img/tc/etfs-01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hskefts.hk%2Fimg%2Ftc%2Fetfs-01.png&h=8ad3c205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方日報報道，土木工程拓展署建議斥資200億至450億元，興建連接洪水橋/厦村新發展區及元朗南新發展區的環保運輸服務系統，提供自動捷運系統、環保巴士系統及現代化電車3個選項。土拓署昨起展開兩個月的公眾諮詢，收集市民對有關運輸系統的意見，評估後定出最終方案。<br />\n<br />\n諮詢期內，土木工程拓展署會於10月19日下午2至5時在天耀社區中心舉辦公眾論壇，又會於該兩個月內在元朗、天水圍及屯門各處舉辦巡迴展覽及流動展覽，並有焦點小組會議。<br />\n<br />\n公眾諮詢摘要<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hskefts.hk/doc/pc1-digest.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hskefts.hk%2Fdoc%2Fpc1-digest.pdf&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGJHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=0c51a307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hskefts.hk/doc/pc1-digest.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年10月16日前，市民可致電研究顧問AECOM或在研究網頁填妥登記表格進行預約。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hskefts.hk/tc/pc.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hskefts.hk%2Ftc%2Fpc.php&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGJHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=2aa93918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hskefts.hk/tc/pc.php</a>"},{"pid":"a34b0c955a9d7b65cba72aa04d833119e28ea058","tid":1615208,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"起碼八年、十年之後先有<br />\n未計delay <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}